Name: Go Ace It
About the game: Go Ace It: Dodge the blue obstacles as you collect points for upgrades and treasured cosmetics! Reach a score previously unseen and become the greatest Ace in history! Progress: Roll through different environments as your skills develop and new levels are unlocked. Learn to conquer the unknown and find new ways to tackle the many challenges this game provides! Leaderboard Once you have mastered your acing skills you will se your position on the leaderboard rise!(TBA) And fear not. This game in NOT pay to win. Your chance of becoming the greatest Acer is equal to everyone else. More to come? This game is in development, and with time, only more features, levels and upgrades will become available for you to accomplish. Hope to see you on our leaderboard in the near future! - DysonGaming
